com.esri.mo2.client.io
Class Crypto

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.client.io.Crypto
public class Crypto
extends Object

This class provides an algorithm for encrypting and decrypting strings to enable secure transfer of service requests and responses, to and from the Application Server.

A sample implementation of this class is shown below:

 Crypto c = new Crypto();
 c.setEncipherRow("KLHJSAFDPGIOYUWQE");
 c.setEncipherColumn("XZVCNBRMETQWKPHIY");
 String dStr = c.Decrypt(c.urlDecode(tmpBuff.toString()), -1);
